CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 9, 1956, pg. A29, reads: "MARBLES CHAMP - Joseph Eugene Gordon, right, of Scully Rd., East End, city marbles champion.... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: 1956 City of Pittsburgh marbles champion, Joseph Eugene Gordon, wearing crown and kneeling on floor with marbles
